                <head>31. Summary of Conclusions for a Deputies Committee Meeting<note n="1"
                        type="source" xml:id="d31fn1">Source: <persName corresp="#p_BGHW_1">George
                            H.W. Bush</persName> Library, <persName corresp="#p_BGHW_1"
                            >Bush</persName> Presidential Records, National Security Council,
                        H-Files, <gloss target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss>/DC Meetings Files, OA/ID
                        90010–013, <gloss target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss>/DC 034—June 12, 1989—<gloss
                            target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss>/DC Meeting on NSR-14 re: U.S. <gloss
                            target="#t_START_1">START</gloss> Positions on New Initiatives. Secret.
                        The meeting took place in the Situation Room.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
